      • createServerChannel

        public ServerChannel createServerChannel(String name,
                                         String topic,
                                         Boolean isPublic,
                                         ServerChannelType type,
                                         String serverId,
                                         String groupId,
                                         Integer categoryId)
        Create a channel in the specified server.
        https://www.guilded.gg/docs/api/channels/ChannelCreate
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the channel (min length 1; max length 100).
        topic - The topic of the channel (max length 512).
        isPublic - Whether the channel can be accessed from users who are not member of the server (default false).
        type - The type of channel to create.
        serverId - The server that the channel should be created in.
        groupId - The group that the channel should be created in (optional). If not provided, channel will be created in the "Server home" group.
        categoryId - The category the channel should go in (optional). If not provided, channel will be a top-level channel.
        Returns:
        The created channel's ServerChannel object.
